title: Avaya Announces Fourth Quarter and Fiscal Year 2015 Reporting Date and Date of Investor Meeting ...
text: ( Source : Avaya Inc) 15 Oct 2015 Santa Clara, Calif. - October, 15 , 2015 -- Avaya announced today that it plans to report results for the fourth fiscal quarter and full fiscal year ending September 30 , 2015 on Wednesday, November 11 , 2015.
